metadata.name: Who's on First NFT 2:21:10
metadata.description: Each NFT in this series of 8,791 NFTs contains a unique still frame image of Abbott & Costello’s performance of Who’s on First from the March 11, 1951 episode of The Colgate Comedy Hour. The NFTs are exclusively licensed from the estates of Bud Abbott and Lou Costello via Unforgettable Licensing.
